TITLE: Using EntityHydrator in a Service
DESCRIPTION: Example of using EntityHydrator in a custom service to hydrate a Product entity with its facetValues and facets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vendure-ecommerce/vendure/blob/master/docs/docs/reference/typescript-api/data-access/entity-hydrator.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
