TITLE: Implementing FacetValueFormInputComponent for Selecting Multiple FacetValues
DESCRIPTION: Component that allows selection of multiple FacetValues via an autocomplete select input. It's designed for use with 'ID' type list fields that represent FacetValue IDs.
